  <front>
   <head>Lirica latina - Lirica XLIV</head>
  </front>
  <body>
   <lg xmlns="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0" type="poem">
    <lg n="1">
     <l n="1">Sis dives, generosa, bella, casta,</l>
     <l n="2">docta, et si ulterius potes quid esse;</l>
     <l n="3">si, Trivultia, non simul benigna es,</l>
     <l n="4">nulli bella places, pudica nulli,</l>
     <l n="5">nulli docta videris, et beatae</l>
     <l n="6">nullos divitiae movent, genusve,</l>
     <l n="7">et si his ulterius potes quid esse.</l>
    </lg>
   </lg>
